name: Dark Parables: The Swan Princess and The Dire Tree
name_original: Dark Parables: The Swan Princess and The Dire Tree
description:
Dark Parables: The Swan Princess and The Dire Tree is a puzzle game developed by Eipix Entertainment. It came out on 06-07-2016. It was published by Big Fish Games.
You can play Dark Parables: The Swan Princess and The Dire Tree on PC.
